OL,3,CHow one school is bucking attendance
OL,4,Ctrends
OL,6,FA school in Caerphilly is making waves
OL,7,Fas it bucks attendance trends with an
OL,8,Falmost perfect record.
OL,10,FYsgol Gymraeg Caerffili consistently
OL,11,Fachieves attendance rates above the
OL,12,Fnational average in Wales, and for the
OL,13,Ffirst month of this academic year,
OL,14,Fachieved a rate of 98.2%.
OL,16,FEleri Jones, Acting Headteacher at
OL,17,FYsgol Gymraeg Caerffili, attributed
OL,18,Fthe school's success to their
OL,19,F"holistic" approach.
