OL,3,CHow one school is bucking attendance
OL,4,Ctrends
OL,6,FMs Jones said: "We take a whole-school
OL,7,Fapproach to improving and maintaining
OL,8,Fattendance, rooted in the
OL,9,Frelationships we build with pupils,
OL,10,Fstaff and families.
OL,12,F"All members of staff, including our
OL,13,FSchool Clerk and Health and Wellbeing
OL,14,FOfficer who carry out the Family
OL,15,FEngagement Officer role, work closely
OL,16,Fwith families, and we communicate any
OL,17,Fconcerns in a positive, supportive
OL,18,Fway. This ensures a truly holistic
OL,19,Fexperience for our learners.
